{"tid":370891,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"沖繩5日4夜自由行行程 求評","createTime":"2017-08-23T09:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T10:02:17.000Z","uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19e2ab0e29a4d252c31b0f322cb77d4773a60731","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"黎緊一月尾去沖繩自由行，第一次去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咁嘅行程o唔ok，希望大家可以俾少少意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打算頭三日會自駕<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 <br />\n坐香港航空06:55飛，10:25到那霸機場<br />\n攞車<br />\n海人食堂&gt;殘波岬&gt;万座毛&gt;名護城夜櫻<br />\n宿 名護<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n古利宇大橋&gt;古利宇島&gt;今歸仁城跡賞&gt;美麗海水族館&gt;返那霸<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n租和服(或浴衣)&gt;與儀公園&gt;八重瀨公園&gt;系滿漁港&gt;還車<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n首里城&gt;國際通<br />\n主要那霸市內自由活動<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 <br />\nOutlet&gt;搭16:00航班回港<br />\n<br />\n本身打算Day 2 skip 今歸仁城跡，去完水族館&gt;泡瀨漁市場&gt;那霸。但時間好似唔太足夠，唯有改為上面行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e960af815b590f25e60754e455473dae6c8fb795","tid":370891,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"第一日，排得隊出關再去攞車都隨時十二點幾一點，揸到去海人食堂為咗食啲丼？<br />\n<br />\n機場附近遊食來已經滿足到你要嘅嘢啦。"},{"pid":"df880314c3e61f3f514d04845af482b65dae5cc8","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一日，排得隊出關再去攞車都隨時十二點幾一點，揸到去海人食堂為咗食啲丼？<br />\n<br />\n機場附近遊食來已經滿足到你要嘅嘢啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係為左去殘波岬，所以去附近嘅海人食堂。<br />\n<br />\n但如果我落左去系滿果邊會唔會多左路？thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db16729d7b273ee3a1b8764579da714dae4c4470","tid":370891,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T14:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一日，排得隊出關再去攞車都隨時十二點幾一點，揸到去海人食堂為咗食啲丼？<br />\n<br />\n機場附近遊食來已經滿足到你要嘅嘢啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係為左去殘波岬，所以去附近嘅海人食堂。<br />\n<br />\n但如果我落左去系滿果邊會唔會多左路？thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你邊間租車？<br />\n<br />\n歐力士機場個車場過去超近。<br />\n<br />\n機場落系滿得幾公里路，揸車唔算兜啦。"},{"pid":"a5ada0b35edd9e793824fc7da85b07d5fc5c9ec4","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一日，排得隊出關再去攞車都隨時十二點幾一點，揸到去海人食堂為咗食啲丼？<br />\n<br />\n機場附近遊食來已經滿足到你要嘅嘢啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係為左去殘波岬，所以去附近嘅海人食堂。<br />\n<br />\n但如果我落左去系滿果邊會唔會多左路？thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你邊間租車？<br />\n<br />\n歐力士機場個車場過去超近。<br />\n<br />\n機場落系滿得幾公里路，揸車唔算兜啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我仲未諗定邊間好，我仲研究緊，不過我有睇過你遊記，都有了解過。因為其實今次都係第一次自駕，所以好多嘢都唔係好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為依家仲同啲朋友研究緊個行程，諗住租車可以唔使咁急就放埋一邊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6231c18b9f6bdaeb2d5d38b12378e6c74930481f","tid":370891,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"岩岩沖繩自駕完 tabirai 租 orix 公司 一個字 平 夠抵玩<br />\n啲車算新 不過無得特定車款"},{"pid":"c982669f7e113a95ce36a0de0b673a60b146746f","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T23:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩沖繩自駕完 tabirai 租 orix 公司 一個字 平 夠抵玩<br />\n啲車算新 不過無得特定車款</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我啱啱上網睇，本身諗住喺OTS租，但我見好多人都話佢偏貴。<br />\n我驚佢冇特定車款，我會唔夠放喼(大型)，三個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a718acca0d5b2c8c60385f2847117efd1b4ccb","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T15:20:55.000Z","msg":"依家行程有少少變動，麻煩俾少少意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 <br />\n坐香港航空06:55飛，10:25到那霸機場<br />\n攞車<br />\n系滿遊食來&gt;万座毛&gt;酒店&gt;晚餐&gt;名護城夜櫻<br />\n宿 名護<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n古利宇大橋&gt;美麗海水族館&gt;海中展覽塔+玻璃船&gt;返那霸<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n泊漁港早餐&gt;租和服(或浴衣)&gt;與儀公園&gt;八重瀨公園&gt;新心都+還車<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n參加賞鯨團<br />\n下午主要那霸市內自由活動<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 <br />\nOutlet&gt;搭16:00航班回港<br />\n<br />\n我第一次自駕，租車都仲諗緊租aqua好冇，唔知三個喼夠唔夠位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麻煩俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d259bacda1c5ab8e239dfae8f3c1bdfe383e411","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ec2e2602f84be164128efb9c76cc6fbdfcf29d","tid":370891,"uid":131063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"Outlet唔去好過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又貴又無野行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過近機場"},{"pid":"55c5d845be6684f55c485e8add84b4d298da1458","tid":370891,"uid":131063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"水族館無乜野行，好似海洋公園睇海豚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3161c56184d917b62e917ccc7020f80c7023250f","tid":370891,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"有無人租過camping 車？<br />\n有床 有廁 有廚房果種<br />\n酒店都唔駛bk， 好正咁<br />\n<br />\n有無包膠 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6574ed06a6d1de9604da30c42a735bba298a7a0b","tid":370891,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩沖繩自駕完 tabirai 租 orix 公司 一個字 平 夠抵玩<br />\n啲車算新 不過無得特定車款</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我啱啱上網睇，本身諗住喺OTS租，但我見好多人都話佢偏貴。<br />\n我驚佢冇特定車款，我會唔夠放喼(大型)，三個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早40日offer , 我次次都ots"},{"pid":"1c5751f56b59b1b57d626188917480a4df771865","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Outlet唔去好過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又貴又無野行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過近機場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為近機場所以一去，唔使諗咁多嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee70274092d7e043c7493db5b4797eaeddf842f","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水族館無乜野行，好似海洋公園睇海豚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n居然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁到時有時間鬆動再去多個景點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為驚行程太趕，太夜。"},{"pid":"794deca39385413fd31d326c8d25a63a4790f005","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩沖繩自駕完 tabirai 租 orix 公司 一個字 平 夠抵玩<br />\n啲車算新 不過無得特定車款</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我啱啱上網睇，本身諗住喺OTS租，但我見好多人都話佢偏貴。<br />\n我驚佢冇特定車款，我會唔夠放喼(大型)，三個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早40日offer , 我次次都ots</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家仲未租，因為我早上11點幾租，但想第三日夜晚還，但佢24小時制，好似計多左日錢，我睇過要13000円多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a806dfaf0eb967eab75f77c39d92fb2e8e614f97","tid":370891,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>水族館無乜野行，好似海洋公園睇海豚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n居然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁到時有時間鬆動再去多個景點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為驚行程太趕，太夜。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水族館主打睇鯨鯊"},{"pid":"1578bc083edd30aff21a791c4c62234a23f6842d","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>水族館無乜野行，好似海洋公園睇海豚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n居然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁到時有時間鬆動再去多個景點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為驚行程太趕，太夜。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水族館主打睇鯨鯊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我預兩個鐘算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afb6c9027e5ff082488a8977010ba9b2f0967ce","tid":370891,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家行程有少少變動，麻煩俾少少意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 <br />\n坐香港航空06:55飛，10:25到那霸機場<br />\n攞車<br />\n系滿遊食來&gt;万座毛&gt;酒店&gt;晚餐&gt;名護城夜櫻<br />\n宿 名護<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n古利宇大橋&gt;美麗海水族館&gt;海中展覽塔+玻璃船&gt;返那霸<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n泊漁港早餐&gt;租和服(或浴衣)&gt;與儀公園&gt;八重瀨公園&gt;新心都+還車<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n參加賞鯨團<br />\n下午主要那霸市內自由活動<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 <br />\nOutlet&gt;搭16:00航班回港<br />\n<br />\n我第一次自駕，租車都仲諗緊租aqua好冇，唔知三個喼夠唔夠位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麻煩俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAqua你收起一個後座就可以放2件29寸+1件27寸"},{"pid":"f6a00060e33e76de3c3818924bf9c0ddeae6d73f","tid":370891,"uid":97929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家行程有少少變動，麻煩俾少少意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 <br />\n坐香港航空06:55飛，10:25到那霸機場<br />\n攞車<br />\n系滿遊食來&gt;万座毛&gt;酒店&gt;晚餐&gt;名護城夜櫻<br />\n宿 名護<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n古利宇大橋&gt;美麗海水族館&gt;海中展覽塔+玻璃船&gt;返那霸<br />\n宿 那霸<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n泊漁港早餐&gt;租和服(或浴衣)&gt;與儀公園&gt;八重瀨公園&gt;新心都+還車<br />\n宿 